- Trading footprint $F_t=I_tQ_t$ measures mark-to-market distortion from internal impact.
- Fire-sale stress tests require both own liquidation impact and external crowding impact.
- Combining two portfolios can reduce costs through internalization and joint optimization, while competitive trading can create an impact arms race.

